ygData.messageBody:
Practice your brass skills. It's probably really, really low. I'm 44, and
just got it into the 130s. I think (not positive), that even if you're
singing it, it checks your brass skill for misses.

The 2 best places to do this, are the arena, or in the cave with the shady
swashbuckler. Just start up fear, and walk away for an hour or 2, or all
night if you care to.

And of course, you're going to get alot because you just got it.

Bien
